item.title: Enigma of Eddie
item.description: Boyd and Josh were joined by friend of the podcast Alan Alger to reflect on an impressive 5-0 victory against rock-bottom Sheffield United as Eddie Nketiah scored his first Premier League hat-trick, but is that enough to convince the doubters? Alan ponders Odegaard’s recents impact, Raya’s ongoing status as the number one keeper, and we look ahead to fixtures against West Ham and Newcastle. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/COMG4945615142
